      "span_id": "p121_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0002",
      "text": " 102",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0003",
      "text": "a)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        57.65,
        114.91,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0004",
      "text": " Payload Length:",
      "bbox": [
        114.91,
        57.65,
        200.37,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0005",
      "text": " Bytes 2-3 of Word 0 contain a 16-bit value that specifies the length M of the",
      "bbox": [
        200.4,
        57.65,
        539.96,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0006",
      "text": "RNFT LS_ACC Payload in bytes.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        69.65,
        269.6,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0007",
      "text": "M = 8 + N*4",
      "bbox": [
        132.0,
        94.97,
        185.32,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0008",
      "text": "where",
      "bbox": [
        132.0,
        118.97,
        159.19,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0009",
      "text": "N is the number of FC-4 Entries contained in the Payload. ",
      "bbox": [
        132.0,
        142.96,
        390.25,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0010",
      "text": "b)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        166.96,
        114.92,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0011",
      "text": " List Length:",
      "bbox": [
        114.92,
        166.96,
        180.1,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0012",
      "text": " Byte 1 of Word 1 contains an 8-bit value that specifies the total number of FC-4",
      "bbox": [
        180.06,
        166.96,
        540.01,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0013",
      "text": "protocols supported by the responder.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        178.96,
        290.72,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0014",
      "text": "If List Length exceeds Index+N then the originator may request additional records with another",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        202.96,
        539.98,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0015",
      "text": "RNFT in which Index is increased by N.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        214.96,
        297.4,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0016",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        238.96,
        114.38,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0017",
      "text": "Index:",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        238.96,
        151.84,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0018",
      "text": " Byte 3 of Word 1 contains an 8-bit value that specifies the index of the first FC-4 Entry",
      "bbox": [
        151.8,
        238.96,
        539.96,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0019",
      "text": "returned in the RNFT reply.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        250.96,
        243.48,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0020",
      "text": "d)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        274.96,
        114.92,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0021",
      "text": " FC-4 Entry:",
      "bbox": [
        114.92,
        274.96,
        176.23,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0022",
      "text": " The FC-4 Entry record contains a FC-4 Entry and is shown in table 106.",
      "bbox": [
        176.28,
        274.96,
        496.15,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0023",
      "text": "A)",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        382.96,
        132.38,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0024",
      "text": " FC-4 Type:",
      "bbox": [
        132.38,
        382.96,
        191.3,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0025",
      "text": " The FC-4 TYPE code of a FC-4 protocol that is supported by the sending",
      "bbox": [
        191.28,
        382.96,
        539.99,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0026",
      "text": "Nx_Port.  The values are defined in FC-FS-2",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        394.96,
        335.73,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0027",
      "text": ".",
      "bbox": [
        335.76,
        394.96,
        338.53,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0028",
      "text": "B)",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        418.96,
        132.38,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0029",
      "text": " FC-4 Qualifier:",
      "bbox": [
        132.38,
        418.96,
        207.27,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0030",
      "text": " The FC-4 Qualifier may be used to distinguish between two protocols that",
      "bbox": [
        207.3,
        418.96,
        540.05,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0031",
      "text": "use the same FC-4 TYPE code.",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        430.96,
        279.06,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0032",
      "text": "For  FC-4 type codes that are reserved or assigned for specific use in this standard {CWC:",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        454.96,
        539.97,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0033",
      "text": "Should this be 00h to DFh?} (00h - 68h), the value of the FC-4 Qualifier shall be zero.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        466.96,
        499.59,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0034",
      "text": "For Vendor specific FC-4 TYPE codes (E0h through FFh), the FC-4 Qualifier shall be selected",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        490.96,
        539.93,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0035",
      "text": "from one of the 24-bit Company_ID values assigned by the IEEE Registration Authority to the",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        502.96,
        540.03,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0036",
      "text": "organization that defines the Vendor specific FC-4 protocol, and that Company_ID shall be",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        514.96,
        539.87,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0037",
      "text": "used to qualify that FC-4 TYPE in all implementations.  It is up to the organization that defines",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        526.96,
        539.99,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0038",
      "text": "the Vendor specific FC-4 protocol to assure that the protocol has a unique qualified FC-4 Type.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        538.96,
        540.06,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0039",
      "text": "4.2.39",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        123.78,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0040",
      "text": "Scan Remote Loop (SRL)",
      "bbox": [
        133.78,
        562.96,
        253.69,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0041",
      "text": "4.2.39.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        192.64,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0042",
      "text": "The SRL ELS shall require a switch to scan attached loops to determine if any L_Ports have been",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.96,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0043",
      "text": "disabled or removed.  If the switch determines any L_Ports that are currently logged in with the Fab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        540.1,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0044",
      "text": "ric have been removed or disabled it shall update the name server and send an RSCN to all regis-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        540.12,
        646.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0045",
      "text": "tered Nx_Ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        165.44,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0046",
      "text": "The SRL Payload indicates whether the switch shall scan all attached loops or a single loop.  If a sin-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        540.07,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p121_s0047",
      "text": "gle loop is to be scanned the Payload shall contain the FL_Port_ID of the loop to be scanned.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        508.72,
        694.13
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
